One benefit to this is that functions which take pointers as arguments can
be annotated with the "nonnull" attribute - `__attribute__((nonnull))` in [GCC](https://gcc.gnu.org/onlinedocs/gcc-4.0.0/gcc/Function-Attributes.html) .
